text: Las Lajas is a corregimiento in San Félix District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It is the seat of San Félix District. It has a land area of and had a population of 1,521 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 2,218; its population as of 2000 was 1,191. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
